feed.title:
The 2015 Special Olympics World Games will be the largest sports and humanitarian event this year. 
The Games will take place on July 25 - August 2, 2015. Become an Official Fan in the Stands. The Fans in the Stands program is a volunteer role that will allow to lead your own team (friends, family, co-workers, church, etc.) to cheer on these amazing athletes! Please come out and show your support in promoting respect, inclusion, and acceptance of people with intellectual disabilities. "Let me win. But if I cannot win, let me brave in the attempt." Opening day Chris @toms_hanks and I will be fans in the stands for this incredible event.... Will you be there? #Positive #specialolympics2015 #PassTheFlame #torchbearer #LosAngeles #FansInTheStands #bethechange #Volunteer #FatFaith #luckyfatman #WorldGames #CowBell #TeamLead
